{
  "texts": [
    "Along the way, they meet friends in each time period who help them to overcome difficulties and advance to the next level.",
    "The ultimate goal of their adventure is to solve a mystery of the Whiskers' magic tailto protect the balance of time and preserve true friendship.",
    "2 Young adult \"Eclipsed Echoes\" In an imaginary world, people have the ability to share memories with others and store them in a collective database.",
    "However, there are people who want to erase or change some memories, because they are traumatic and unpleasant.",
    "This leads to the appearance of the Memory Outlaws, a group that protects such memories, called Eclipsed Echoes, from any corruption."
  ]
}